Summer Flounder

Source: R/datasets.R
sum_fl.Rd

A dataset containing containing the number of fish caught at different sites and timepoints.

Usage

sum_fl

Format

A data.frame with 350 rows and 13 columns:

patch

Patch code

lat_floor

Lowest latitute associated with the current patch

year

Year

y

Number of fish caught

n_hauls

Number of hauls used to catch the fish

stemp

Sea surface temperature

ssalin

Sea surface salinity

btemp

Sea bottom temperature

bsalin

Sea bottom salinity

lat

Avg. latitude

lon

Avg. longitude

depth

Avg. depth

area_km2

Area in km^2^

Source

https://www.fisheries.noaa.gov/feature-story/2022-fall-bottom-trawl-survey-completed-northeast
